videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald keeps it himself and finds his way into the end zone to give the Bulldogs a 13-3 lead heading into the second half.
videos.headline: Mississippi State punches it in before halftime

videos.description: Marlon Davidson jumps the line to deflect Jace Christmann's 31-yard field goal attempt.
videos.headline: Auburn blocks Mississippi State FG

videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald's 21-yard score puts the Tigers up 23-9 and also passes Tim Tebow for most rushing yards in SEC history by a quarterback.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald breaks Tebow's SEC QB rushing record
